{"tid":2461037,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"賀錦麗登機時無視衛兵敬禮遭批傲慢","createTime":"2021-03-25T07:47:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T08:23:23.000Z","uid":28765,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"52a96948354edacbb643b7fd0766a2f5ae9605a5","tid":2461037,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T07:47:40.000Z","msg":"〔編譯陳成良／綜合報導〕美國總統搭機向衛兵敬禮，被視為最高統帥尊重軍人的傳統，該傳統也成了副總統一項不成文慣例。不過現任副總統賀錦麗被媒體拍到多次搭乘「空軍二號」（副總統專機）時，當班的空軍士官向她敬禮，她卻視若無物沒回禮，態度傲慢遭到非議。<br />\n<br />\n《福斯新聞》24日在報導中，彙整了賀錦麗最近4次乘專機不甩敬禮的影片，並強調前副總統彭斯都不會忘了這個基本禮儀。<br />\n<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n消息傳出後，美國國防部連忙幫賀錦麗緩頰，強調副總統不是美軍指揮體系的一環，賀錦麗無需向軍人回禮。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，美國也沒有明文規定總統乘機必須向衛兵回禮，這項傳統始於前總統雷根時代，並為往後的正副總統所遵循。<br />\n<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3478662\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3478662&d=Vr1Lb3BWhK3V%2BSmIqtN%2B%2Fs70t8psI8cu6Rjg0MoA49o%3D&h=6fed301b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3478662&h=7e8996f6\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3478662</a>"},{"pid":"4fcdb8d1ec7bda53f3dc40da9076809e99fa8344","tid":2461037,"uid":156652,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T07:49:21.000Z","msg":"呢條白痴婆"},{"pid":"e4228949986e16321d2679be9abecf3441f250b3","tid":2461037,"uid":70487,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T07:50:01.000Z","msg":"賀錦鯉 : 你係我隻兵嚟咋！"},{"pid":"9799853192c501fa5227c8605d41da176eb69c65","tid":2461037,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T07:51:48.000Z","msg":"Tag翻 BLM 咪得囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e7c968848d45041f7bdcc09c06394488cdfdd96","tid":2461037,"uid":104035,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T07:52:11.000Z","msg":"你都On9點解要同你敬禮？<br />\n我係黑人又係女人，再嘈